{"word":"κηλίς","slug":"κηλίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κηλίς</b></el> <el>(κηλί¯ς, ῖδος, ἡ,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a stain, spot, defilement</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> of blood, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>a stain, blemish, dishonour</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}